As he left the space-time vortex, Daemos finally saw the goal of his long 
journey. The Earth. The shiny jewel that will bring the the Tripredacus to 
their destiny! But before any of this, he had to land, and try to find the 
lieutenant.
Daemos: Computer, scan the third planet of the system for this energy 
signature.
He entered a small disk in a reader. The cpu immediatly marked a spot on his 
geographical display.
Daemos: Great!! Now, my friend, we are finally reunited!! Computer, plot 
course and engage autopilot!
